<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/master.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/studySearch.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bowser/2.11.0/bundled.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/studySearch.js"></script>
    <title>ALEX</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include('../../partials/header'); %>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <img class="logo" src="/images/logo.png" /> 
        <h1 class="title">Results</h1>
        <p> Thank you for all that information! Here are some research studies we found for you.</p>
        <p> After you’ve downloaded your “Liked Studies”, please click the following button to continue to our survey. </p>
    
        <% for(var i=0; i<trialsList.length; i++) { %>
            <div class="study-card">
                <h3><%= trialsList[i].BriefTitle %> </h3>
                <h4>Brief Summary*:</h4>
                <p><%= trialsList[i].GPTSummary %></p>
                <hr/>
                <div class="study-row">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h4>Condition(s): </h4>
                        <p><%= trialsList[i].Condition %></p>
                    </div>
                   <div class="row">
                    <h4>Intervention/Treatment:</h4>
                    <p><%= trialsList[i].InterventionType %> </p>
                   </div>
                   <div class="row">
                    <h4>Study Type:</h4>
                    <p><%= trialsList[i].StudyType %></p>
                   </div>
                </div>
                <hr/>
                <div class="study-row">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h4>Study Location: </h4>
                        <p><%= trialsList[i].Condition %></p>
                    </div>
                   <div class="row">
                    <h4>Study Contact:</h4>
                    <p>Name: <%= trialsList[i].CentralContactName[0] %> </p>
                    <p>Email: <%= trialsList[i].CentralContactEMail[0] %> </p>
                   </div>
                </div>
                <p>If you're interested in this study, click the button below to copy text to email the central contact!</p>
                <button onclick="copyEmailText(`<%= trialsList[i].CentralContactName[0] %>`, `<%= trialsList[i].BriefTitle %>`, `<%= trialsList[i].GPTSummary%>`)">Copy Email Text</button>
                <p>*This summary was prepared by the ALEX Research Team. See the full study description at: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://clinicaltrials.gov/study/<%= trialsList[i].NCTId[0] %>">https://clinicaltrials.gov/study/<%= trialsList[i].NCTId[0] %></a></p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>